        <para>The U-Bolts on the fixed lift axle assembly must be tightened and torqued using the following cross
            pattern sequence (refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f14019p">FIGURE 53</hotlnk>
            <xref refid="f14019p"/>):
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten nut #1 and nut #2 to partial torque,</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten nut #3 and nut #4 to partial torque,</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Repeat steps 1 and 2 tightening all four nuts to full torque.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f14019p" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic id="g14019p" filename="../figg14/G14019P.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitheight="152px"
